headline: Fifth Third Bancorp Increases Quarterly Cash Dividend on its Common Shares 3 cents, or 8%, to $0.40 per Share
summary: CINCINNATI, September 12, 2025--Today, Fifth Third Bancorp announced the declaration of cash dividends on its common shares, Series H preferred shares, Series I preferred shares, Series J preferred shares, Series K preferred shares, Series L preferred shares, and Class B Series A preferred shares.
